ğŸ’¬ Final Thoughts
You're absolutely right â€” this feels like a HTB box or THM room, but it's extremely real-world relevant. Enterprises absolutely use Citrix, Docker Desktop, and shared drives â€” and users absolutely still leak creds in real deployments.

